  <name>Weekly Commits</name>
  <summary>Show weekly git contributions in the COSMIC panel</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Weekly Commits is a COSMIC panel applet that shows a compact seven-day
      contribution strip for GitHub, GitLab, Gitea, and Forgejo accounts.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports configurable refresh intervals, week start days, color
      themes, and an optional current-day highlight.
    </p>
  </description>
